Winthorp's Mansion PC

Genre:First-Person Shooter
Release Date:November 12, 2000
Publisher:Crystal Interactive

Synopsis by T.J. Deci

Take on the role of private eye Dick Usher and guide him through a world of hidden clues and strange surprises in Winthrop's Mansion. The mystery adventure takes place in the spooky old house, full of fast action and lots of bad guys to shoot. The hero begins with a .38 caliber, but more weapons become available as the game moves forward. Some weapons are more effective than others in certain situations. As players progress they will find that there is more to the strange mansion than meets the eye, perhaps as they become lost in the huge labyrinth or discover the pirate ship, located many levels below the surface.


